parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure due to Manufacturing Defect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause sudden loss of power, stalling, and even accidents, putting the driver and passengers at risk.
symptoms: smoke coming out from under the dash

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling due to Various Causes
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine stalling can cause loss of control, accidents, and leave the driver stranded.
EGR valve failure can cause engine stalling, loss of power, and decreased fuel efficiency.
Clutch and hydraulic system failure can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
and the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can lead to serious injury or fatalities, as the airbag is designed to provide critical protection to occupants in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag light on the instrument panel
airbag failure to deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag warning light coming on can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident.
symptoms: light will come on and stay on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clockspring can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag light on the instrument panel

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake proportioning valve can cause extended stopping distances, increasing the risk of accidents.
The failure of the ABS can cause loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: failure of the brakes to engage

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbags to deploy can result in serious injury or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake discs and pads can cause reduced braking performance, increasing the risk of accidents.
